  "analyst_note": "CVE-2019-7609: Prototype pollution leading to RCE via Timelion visualizations in Kibana. Affects 5.x before 5.6.15 and 6.x before 6.6.1. The /api/status endpoint returns JSON including the Kibana version as {\"version\":{\"number\":\"6.5.4\",...}}. Kibana typically runs on port 5601. The exploit requires access to the Kibana interface \u2014 if Kibana is internet-exposed, this is critical priority. Fix: upgrade to 5.6.15, 6.6.1, or 7.x.",
